<h2>Tailor made wine trips</h2>

<p>Bleu Vins takes you off the beaten track to uncover the Loire Valley secrets and its wines. We design your own customized trip in Anjou, Saumur or Touraine regions.<br class='autobr' />
Depending on your preferences, your needs and your budget, our knowledge of the region will ensure you to live a unique experience with family or friends.</p>
</div>
</div>

<p><br/></p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
    <img src="/images/authentic.jpg" alt="Authentic">
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-9">
<h2>Authentic</h2>

<p>Get away and dive into the authentic Loire Valley. By choosing Bleu Vins, you will discover the real identity of the Loire Valley vineyards and meet with the locals. Enjoy the Loire Valley heritage, traditions, history and gastronomy spending few days away. <br class='autobr' />
Your stay will be a unique experience, take a break of your daily life and live new experiences with Bleu Vins.</p>
</div>
</div>

<p><br/></p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
    <img src="/images/all-languages-welcome.jpg" alt="All languages welcome">
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-9">
<h2>All languages welcome</h2>

<p>Because the Loire Valley is a place not to be missed Bleu Vins team and our partners welcome you in french, English and many others languages on request (dutch, german, portuguese, Spanish…)<br class='autobr' />
Wherever you come from, the Loire Valley and its vineyards won’t have any secrets for you!</p>
</div>
</div>

<p><br/></p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
    <img src="/images/for-every-budgets.jpg" alt="For every budgets">
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-9">
<h2>For every budgets</h2>

<p>Because we wish the wine tourism to be experience by many people, we offer stays covering a wide range of prices and services. Whether you want to participate in an half day wine experience or a 3-day stay Prestige wine tasting trip, there is something to suit all tastes!</p>
</div>
